{
  "stem": "833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- he said to me, Herbert, it seems to me that you want to be taking music as a profession.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, you are guessing right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I just want to tell you that-- I don't want to talk you out of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I just want to tell you what the problems are, I mean, what the financial problems are, what the social problems are, what's-- what's in store, and how hard it is-- that music-- the study of music is much more intricate than any other study.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I learned at that the time, clearly, what he-- he said that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was very-- very observing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He said, if you learn in high school your mathematics, your algebra, your-- your geometry, and so forth, you can go to the technical high school, to the technical college, and in four years, you'll get a diploma that you're a good engineer-- that you can do.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You cannot go and do all these things that you need to learn as an-- as an educated person and then go to college and say, I want to learn the violin.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You have to start as you started, he said, when you are a very small kid.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You have to grow up with the music.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You have to become-- music, as he-- he knew it-- music is a much more complicated and a much more demanding thing than any other of the things.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Maybe, he said, maybe medicine may be that difficult.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you have to face a very hard study in addition to what you do with everybody else-- I mean your Latin, your algebra, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he didn't scare me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he felt it was important to tell me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm not-- when I decided, yes, then I had his support.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
